sentence: can you tell me what aircraft is used for delta flight twelve twenty two <from> <salt> <lake> ci- from kansas city to salt lake city
sq2:
SELECT DISTINCT  '"'||v1.aircraft_code||'"', '"'||v2.aircraft_code_sequence||'"',
 '"'||v2.airline_code||'"', '"'||v3.airport_code||'"',
 '"'||v4.city_code||'"', '"'||v4.city_name||'"',
 '"'||v5.airport_code||'"', '"'||v6.city_code||'"', '"'||v6.city_name||'"',
 v2.flight_number, '"'||v2.flight_id||'"' FROM aircraft v0,
 equipment_sequence v1, flight v2, airport_service v3,
 city v4, airport_service v5, city v6 
WHERE ((v0.aircraft_code = ANY v1.aircraft_code) 
AND ((v1.aircraft_code_sequence = ANY v2.aircraft_code_sequence) 
AND ((v2.airline_code = 'DL') 
AND (((v2.from_airport = ANY v3.airport_code) 
AND ((v3.city_code = ANY v4.city_code) AND (v4.city_name = 'KANSAS CITY'))) 
AND (((v2.to_airport = ANY v5.airport_code) 
AND ((v5.city_code = ANY v6.city_code) AND (v6.city_name = 'SALT LAKE CITY'))) 
AND (v2.flight_number =  1222))))));
